PS C:\>  C:\PS  Import-Module ActiveDirectory
C:\PS  $users = foreach ( $user in Get-ADGroupMember  MyGroup  ) { echo ($user.name +  @mycompany.com ); }
C:\PS  Get-FasServerForUser -UserPrincipalNames $users  Description   This enumerates the UPN addresses of users in "MyGroup" and looks up the FAS servers that will hold cached certificates for each.
